{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Gatsby Starter Blog","author":"Kyle Mathews"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"74145268-f484-5f59-8e16-266881758807","excerpt":"indexnode와 npmpackage.json과 package-lock.json트랜스 컴파일러 babellint 프로그램 eslintgatsby로 블로그 시작하기gatsby-cli 설치하기터미널에서 다음 명령어를 사용하여 gatsby-cli…","html":"<h3>index</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#node%EC%99%80-npm\">node와 npm</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#packagejson%EA%B3%BC-package-lockjson\">package.json과 package-lock.json</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%8A%A4-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%9F%AC-babel\">트랜스 컴파일러 babel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lint-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%A8-eslint\">lint 프로그램 eslint</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>gatsby로 블로그 시작하기</h3>\n<h4>gatsby-cli 설치하기</h4>\n<p>터미널에서 다음 명령어를 사용하여 gatsby-cli를 전역에 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g gatsby-cli</code></pre></div>\n<h4>사이트 생성하기</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ gatsby new <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>생성할 사이트 이름<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>기본으로 가져올 소스코드 주소<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>br<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이 명령어를 통해 개츠비에서 제공하는 기본구조의 사이트를 쉽게 생성할 수 있습니다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">기본으로 가져올 소스코드 주소</code>를 명시하지 않으면 <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-default\">https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-default</a> 에 작성된 소스코드가 받아집니다.</p>\n<p>저는 블로그가 목적이니 블로그 스타터를 사용했습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ gatsby new react-blog https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-blog</code></pre></div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/349eb/gatsby_blog_1-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 87.05985915492958%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Chinese Salty Egg\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/b9e4f/gatsby_blog_1-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/cf440/gatsby_blog_1-1.png 148w,\n/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/d2d38/gatsby_blog_1-1.png 295w,\n/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/b9e4f/gatsby_blog_1-1.png 590w,\n/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/f9b6a/gatsby_blog_1-1.png 885w,\n/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/2d849/gatsby_blog_1-1.png 1180w,\n/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/bbefa/gatsby_blog_1-1.png 1770w,\n/static/1815aa8e04da3918fa0a31128d785161/349eb/gatsby_blog_1-1.png 2272w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>github.io 주소 사용하기</h3>\n<p>다음 명령어를 실행하여 package.json에 devDependencies를 추가해줍니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gh-pages --save-dev</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"deploy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby build --prefix-paths &amp;&amp; gh-pages -d public\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>참고</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/quick-start\">Gatsby Docs</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"react gatsby로 github 블로그 만들기!","date":"May 02, 2019","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/dev/gatsby_blog/1/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/hi-folks/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"New Beginnings"}},"next":null}}